                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus target="#18vb">ff. 18vb-19</locus>ra: Donation note.  <quote xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <quote xml:lang="en"/>
                           The note is poorly readably since the red ink faded off. The note states that the Ms. Gadla Giyorgis and Tasfā Māryām purchased the Ms. with their own money and donated it to church of Dabra Maʿṣo. Condemnatio mentions <roleName type="title">ʾabuna</roleName> salāma who is probably Metropolitan salāma III (in tenure 1841-67).
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
